Brazil May Probe ‘Irregularity’ in FDI Inflows, Estado Says

-- B y   I u r i   D a n t a s
-- 
2011-03-24T14:29:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/brazil-may-probe-irregularity-in-fdi-inflows-estado-says.html
Brazil ’s government suspects
“irregularity” in inflows registered as foreign direct
investment and may ask the tax agency to open a probe, Estado de
S.Paulo newspaper reported without saying how it obtained the
information.  A spokesman at the  Finance Ministry  wasn’t immediately
available to comment when called by Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
